  Workflow
  Manage workflow files, jobs, and manual triggers directly.

  Type to search workflows
› Background Tasks               Insert a background task snapshot into the transcript. /ps shows
                                 the same live workflow state.
  director - Edit workflow.yaml  Open manual.yaml in your editor.
  director - summarize           Workflow job
  director - notify              Workflow job
  director - review_backlog      Manual trigger · Enabled
  director - triage              Manual trigger · Enabled

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
